review_blob: This beer could easily be confused with mineral water in my sampling of it, little to no taste and excessive fizz.
I am no gourmet beer drinker by any mean, but I found this to be a pleasing if not jumping-out-at-me drink. Althought it is defineatley better than Beez Neez, it actually resembles honey.
beer_name: Barossa Valley Bee Sting Honey Wheat Beer
